The game engine runs on a \*\*repeating operational cycle\*\*.



\## Simulation Loop



Each cycle contains:



1\. Events / Information  

2\. Player Decisions  

3\. Resource Allocation  

4\. Execution  

5\. Outcome Resolution  

6\. State Update



---



